here are the basics of dating - 

- time is your best friend; allow time to cure everything, even the first knowing of female friends, let time show you the way, naturally;
- naturally, not forcing any thing, that is the key;
- be nice, try to be helpful, these maximize your chance;
- when there is burst of love and feel, let her know;
- she may not respond innitially, but she listens, no matter what you say;
- remmember this: do not, never not hurry. take your time, allow her time, let time show your way; and time will show you the way;
- if nothing happens, walk away;
